releases.name: The one with NSIS.
releases.body:
Basically, I'm now using NSIS for building as it is far superior to squirrel.windows and has less issues.  
You'll need to re-download the application as its effectively an entire new application. It'll still auto-update however.  
(See [electron-userland/electron-packager#529](https://github.com/electron-userland/electron-builder/issues/529) if you want more info on this.  
Sorry for any inconvenience caused!
